question: Count the number of documents that use the PPT template type.
farsi_question: تعداد اسنادی را که از نوع قالب PPT استفاده می‌کنند شمارش کنید.
gold_sql: SELECT count(*) FROM Documents AS T1 JOIN Templates AS T2 ON T1.Template_ID  =  T2.Template_ID WHERE T2.Template_Type_Code  =  'PPT'
predicted_sql:
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Documents.Document_ID)
FROM Documents
JOIN Templates ON Documents.Template_ID = Templates.Template_ID
JOIN Ref_Template_Types ON Templates.Template_Type_Code = Ref_Template_Types.Template_Type_Code
WHERE lower(Ref_Template_Types.Template_Type_Description) ILIKE '%ppt%'

question: For each language, list the number of TV Channels that use it.
farsi_question: برای هر زبان، تعداد کانال‌های تلویزیونی که از آن استفاده می‌کنند را فهرست کنید.
gold_sql: SELECT LANGUAGE ,  count(*) FROM TV_Channel GROUP BY LANGUAGE
predicted_sql:
SELECT "Language", COUNT(*) AS "Number_of_Channels"
FROM "TV_Channel"
GROUP BY "Language"
ORDER BY "Number_of_Channels" DESC;

question: What are the package options and the name of the series for the TV Channel that supports high definition TV?
farsi_question: گزینه‌های بسته و نام سریال برای کانال تلویزیونی که از تلویزیون با کیفیت بالا پشتیبانی می‌کند چیست؟
gold_sql: SELECT package_option ,  series_name FROM TV_Channel WHERE hight_definition_TV  =  "yes"
predicted_sql:
SELECT TV_Channel.Package_Option, TV_Channel.series_name
FROM TV_Channel
WHERE lower(TV_Channel.Hight_definition_TV) ILIKE '%yes%' OR lower(TV_Channel.Hight_definition_TV) ILIKE '%true%' OR lower(TV_Channel.Hight_definition_TV) ILIKE '%supported%'
ORDER BY TV_Channel.series_name;

question: Find the number of flights landing in the city of Aberdeen or Abilene.
farsi_question: تعداد پروازهای فرود در شهر آبردین یا آبیلین را پیدا کنید.
gold_sql: SELECT count(*) FROM Flights AS T1 JOIN Airports AS T2 ON T1.DestAirport  =  T2.AirportCode WHERE T2.city  =  "Aberdeen" OR T2.city  =  "Abilene"
predicted_sql:
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM flights
JOIN airports AS source ON flights.SourceAirport = source.AirportCode
JOIN airports AS dest ON flights.DestAirport = dest.AirportCode
WHERE lower(dest.City) ILIKE '%aberdeen%' OR lower(dest.City) ILIKE '%abilene%'

question: Show the names of singers that have more than one song.
farsi_question: Show the names of singers that have more than one song.
gold_sql: SELECT T1.Name FROM singer AS T1 JOIN song AS T2 ON T1.Singer_ID  =  T2.Singer_ID GROUP BY T1.Name HAVING COUNT(*)  >  1
predicted_sql:
SELECT DISTINCT s.Name
FROM singer s
JOIN song so ON s.Singer_ID = so.Singer_ID
GROUP BY s.Singer_ID, s.Name
HAVING COUNT(so.Song_ID) > 1
ORDER BY s.Name;

predicted_sql:

FROM singer s

question: What is maximum and minimum death toll caused each time?
farsi_question: حداکثر و حداقل تلفات هر بار چقدر است؟
predicted_sql:
SELECT
    ship.name AS ship_name,
    MIN(death.killed) AS min_casualties,
    MAX(death.killed) AS max_casualties
FROM
    ship
JOIN
    death ON ship.id = death.caused_by_ship_id
GROUP BY
    ship.name
ORDER BY
    max_casualties DESC;

question: Show the property type descriptions of properties belonging to that code.

gold_sql: SELECT T2.property_type_description FROM Properties AS T1 JOIN Ref_Property_Types AS T2 ON T1.property_type_code  =  T2.property_type_code GROUP BY T1.property_type_code
predicted_sql:

question: What are the names of properties that are either houses or apartments with more than 1 room?
farsi_question: نام املاکی که خانه یا آپارتمان با بیش از یک اتاق هستند چیست؟
gold_sql: SELECT property_name FROM Properties WHERE property_type_code  =  "House" UNION SELECT property_name FROM Properties WHERE property_type_code  =  "Apartment" AND room_count  >  1
predicted_sql:
SELECT DISTINCT Properties.property_name
FROM Properties
JOIN Ref_Property_Types ON Properties.property_type_code = Ref_Property_Types.property_type_code
WHERE (Ref_Property_Types.property_type_description ILIKE '%house%' OR Ref_Property_Types.property_type_description ILIKE '%apartment%' OR Ref_Property_Types.property_type_description ILIKE '%خانه%' OR Ref_Property_Types.property_type_description ILIKE '%آپارتمان%')
AND Properties.room_count > 1
ORDER BY Properties.property_name;

question: Give me all the information about hiring.
farsi_question: تمام اطلاعات مربوط به استخدام را به من بدهید.
predicted_sql:
SELECT
    employee.Employee_ID,
    employee.Name,
    employee.Age,
    employee.City,
    shop.Shop_ID,
    shop.Name AS Shop_Name,
    shop.Location,
    shop.District,
    shop.Number_products,
    shop.Manager_name,
    hiring.Start_from,
    hiring.Is_full_time
FROM
    hiring
JOIN
    employee ON hiring.Employee_ID = employee.Employee_ID
JOIN
    shop ON hiring.Shop_ID = shop.Shop_ID
ORDER BY
    hiring.Start_from DESC;
